snippet.title: THE RAREST SLIME IS BACK! - Slime Rancher Wiggly Wonderland Update
snippet.description:
Wiggly Wonderland Update is back with new stuff to unlock. The Twinkle Slime is here to spread Christmas cheer and give us a bunch of Chimes to make music with!

MORE SLIME RANCHER VIDEOS: http://bit.ly/PartyGordoUpdate

Hope you enjoyed this Let's Play Slime Rancher video!

Don't forget to hit like and share the video!

►SUBSCRIBE for new videos: http://bit.ly/1EtkvKk
►FOLLOW me on Twitter: http://twitter.com/fynnpire
►CHECK out my photos on Instagram: https://instagram.com/fynnpire

Download Slime Rancher: http://store.steampowered.com/app/433340/


INTRO/OUTRO MUSIC: Fall into My Arms & Glitz at the Ritz 2 from EpidemicSound.com
